Purpose: Create MovieDB using MariaDB included in XAMPP

This script has been tested on XAMPP using Debian 9 or OSX High Sierra. 
Script assumes that the default root password has not been changed since installation. 
Script assumes that XAMPP was installed in the default locations.

DEBIAN:
To execute the script, open folder in terminal:
chmod -x Debian_makedb.sh
sh ./Debian_makedb.sh

OSX:
To execute the script, open folder in terminal:
chmod -x MakeDB.sh
sh ./OSX_makedb.sh

To check tables, either use terminal or check http://localhost/phpmyadmin


